You can allow the mapping of incoming JSON to be case insensitive using the following [feature](https://fasterxml.github.io/jackson-databind/javadoc/2.5/com/fasterxml/jackson/databind/MapperFeature.html#ACCEPT_CASE_INSENSITIVE_PROPERTIES) (only available in Jackson 2.5 and after). See also [this thread](https://stackoverflow.com/q/26058854/16034206) which gives other possible solutions.

